Computes Python style division of `x` by `y`.

### Aliases:

* `tf.compat.v1.divide`
* `tf.compat.v1.math.divide`
* `tf.compat.v2.divide`
* `tf.compat.v2.math.divide`

    x,
    y,
    name=None
